column2: SELECT ra FROM mydb.target_galaxies2 WHERE idx_num = @cnt)   DECLARE @dec1 FLOAT = (SELECT dec FROM mydb.target_galaxies2 WHERE idx_num = @cnt)   DECLARE @theta1 FLOAT = (SELECT theta FROM mydb.target_galaxies2 WHERE idx_num = @cnt)   DECLARE @z1 FLOAT = (SELECT z FROM mydb.target_galaxies2 WHERE idx_num = @cnt) --  DECLARE @name NVARCHAR(#); --    SET @name = &&& + @cnt        SELECT RAND #     p.ra,     p.dec,     z.z,     z.zErr,     p.petroMag_r      --  INTO mydb.   FROM PhotoObj p   JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(@ra1,@dec1,@theta1) n ON n.objID = p.objID   JOIN Photoz z ON z.objID = n.objID    WHERE     p.type = #     AND z.z < @z1 + #*z.zErr     AND z.z > @z1 - #*z.zErr     AND z.zErr < #     AND p.ra BETWEEN # and #     AND p.dec BETWEEN # and #        SET @cnt = @cnt + #; END;
